{"tid":761701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳啟宗：中美貿易戰令香港受益","createTime":"2018-07-30T15:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T15:22:13.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fe4c975563acb8fd0af4fe801cf5a07270cc37","tid":761701,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"　恆隆董事長陳啟宗補充，貿易戰短期令匯率波動，未來６個月匯率走勢「天曉得」，但認為對今年業績不會有太大影響，他又指，下半年外圍因素亦難料，因為事情發生得很快，而貿易戰並非只是中美的事，而是全世界也受影響，但相信事情並非不能逆轉，相信貿易問題可以解決，而長遠而言，中美貿易磨擦或影響香港ＧＤＰ　０﹒１％至０﹒２％，不過很多人因此對美國營商環境失去信心，或會令企業來港上市，令香港從其他方面得益，可以「冷手執個熱煎堆」。"},{"pid":"ef5edf9bcbeedb29886ea18cb0b18f9d4d21760a","tid":761701,"uid":163350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fd779e31e88ae2d343505b286ecc65208773673","tid":761701,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:11:28.000Z","msg":"呢排C9買生果都平咗<br />\n香港已成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b87daa50d7a266f7497b64558de623f2c84053","tid":761701,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/G1Zu26ae7mZr2/giphy.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FG1Zu26ae7mZr2%2Fgiphy.gif%20&h=56d98651&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad2c6e2cebab4b86bfe6b9b0ee24a72e5b9c269","tid":761701,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"香港或成最大贏家"}]}